Guild Levels and Advancement
Ninja guild level and Ninja rank are separate. Guild level unlocks abilities
and rises only when the <Training Master> accepts proof of a newly completed
<mark>. General experience and GXP are never spent on guild level. The final
guild level is 50.

Ninja rank is earned with GXP. Every rank costs 250 GXP and every rank after
rank 1 supplies one training session. Rank never raises guild level. See
<abilities> for training and <marks> for assassination advancement.
